{"title":"Wunduniik","description":"This modlist is a heavy \u002B3000 mods list based on my personnal preferences. It improves almost everything from the vanilla game to make it looks more like a 2025 game than a 2011 game. Keep in mind that the list is more like a vanilla rework than a list adding new quests, new lands... Wunduniik is a draconic word meaning Traveler. I chose this one as I think that when you travel, you discover new cultures, architectures... things can look a lot different. I think this modlist will provide you the same feeling, because you will almost discover a new game.","author":"Alaxouche","maintainers":["github/Alaxouche"],"game":"SkyrimSpecialEdition","official":true,"tags":["Featured"],"nsfw":false,"utility_list":false,"image_contains_title":true,"DisplayVersionOnlyInInstallerView":false,"force_down":false,"links":{"image":"https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/1704/images/89632/89632-1772114072-694182756.png","readme":"https://theastralforge.com/wunduniik/installation-guide/index","download":"https://authored-files.wabbajack.org/Wunduniik.wabbajack_52647dc7-15d7-4675-9ce3-ddb719e41a9d","machineURL":"Wunduniik","discordURL":"https://discord.gg/vKuB7nazBk","websiteURL":"https://theastralforge.com","nexusCollection":null},"download_metadata":{"Hash":{},"Size":749267943,"NumberOfArchives":4696,"SizeOfArchives":209604979754,"NumberOfInstalledFiles":383164,"SizeOfInstalledFiles":365673439921,"TotalSize":575278419675},"version":"6.8.1.0","dateCreated":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","dateUpdated":"2026-01-14T11:07:59.4999093Z","repositoryName":"Wunduniik"}